<TEXT>
<P>
DAMASCUS, August 5 (Xinhua) -- Finnish Foreign Minister Tarja
Halonen and her entourage wound up a two-day visit to Syria and
left here this afternoon for Beirut to continue their tour of the
Middle East.
</P>
<P>
