E.U. aim is to establish peace among the countries in the region.
</P>
<P>
"Our position toward the Middle East peace process is different
from that of the United States as some of the E.U. members are
located in the Mideterranean basin," she said, adding that
"stability and prosperity serve the interests of the region as a
whole."
</P>
<P>
Halonen expressed the will of the E.U. to continue its
unremitting efforts to strengthen the economic and trade ties
with the countries of the region. 
