<HEADLINE> Women's Singles Results at Table Tennis Worlds (Complete) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
EINDHOVEN, Netherlands, August 5 (Xinhua) -- Following are the
women's singles fourth round results at the world table tennis
championships here Thursday afternoon:
</P>
<P>
Zhang Yining, China, bt Ni Xia Lian, Luxembourg, 21-8, 21-17, 21-12
</P>
<P>
Li Ju, China, bt Steff Mihaela, Romania, 21-9, 21-10, 21-17
