<HEADLINE> Sweden Reaffirms One-China Policy </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, August 6 (Xinhua) -- Swedish Foreign Minister Anna
Lindh Friday reaffirmed that her government will continue to
pursue one-China policy.
</P>
