agreement in June 1992 on a joint project of integrated rural
development, law enforcement and drug demand reduction in
Myanmar's Tachilek, Ahdec and Hsanlu areas, and it was
successfully implemented in the three-year period from 1993 to
1996.
</P>
<P>
