a loss of 70 cents to close at 16.00 Singapore dollars. SIA lost
50 cents to finish at 15.30 Singapore dollars. NatElec and UOB F
retreated 40 cents each to end at 7.45 and 11.20 Singapore dollars
respectively.
</P>
