thirsty, and the children continue to die," they wrote. "We urge
you to use your influence to bring happiness, joy, and food to
children in Iraq, to make this world more peaceful and just, and
to put into practice the mandate dictated by the United Nations
last December, in its historic vote declaring the next decade to
be one promoting a culture of nonviolence." 
