<HEADLINE> Indian Railway Minister's resignation accepted </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, August 6 (Xinhua) -- Indian President K. R.
Narayanan accepted the resignation of Railway Minister Nitish
Kumar from the cabinet Thursday night, an official news release
said Friday.
</P>
