<HEADLINE> Results of Sanex Trophy WTA Tournament </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, August 5 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results
Thursday of the Sanex Trophy WTA Tour tournament at Knokke,
Belgium (prefix number denotes seedings):
</P>
<P>
Singles:
</P>
<P>
Second round:
</P>
<P>
2-Silvija Talaja, Croatia, bt Angeles Montolio, Spain, 6-4,6-2
</P>
<P>
3-Karina Habsudova, Slovakia, bt Angelika Bachmann, Germany, 7-
6 (7-3), 6-0
</P>
<P>
4-Maria Antonia Sanchez-Lorenzo, Spain, bt Rita Kuti Kis,
Hungary, 7-6 (8-6), 7-6 (10-8)
</P>
<P>
Mariam Ramon, Spain, bt 8-Laurence Coutois, Belgium, 5-7, 6-3,
7-6 (7-3)
</P>
